   *A Primer on Scientific Programming with Python*.
   Springer, 2009.

.. [Osnes:98] H. Osnes and H. P. Langtangen.
   An efficient probabilistic finite element method for stochastic 
   groundwater flow.
   *Advances in Water Resources*, vol 22, 185-195, 1998.

